com.fortify.bugtracker.common.tgt.context

Interface IContextBugTracker


  • public interface IContextBugTracker
    This interface can be used with the Context.as(Class) method to allow easy access to bugtracker-related information. For now this is just an empty interface that is extended by target-specific Context interfaces.

    Ruud Senden
